/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%C3%A3ng-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-l%C3%A2u-di%C3%AAn-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BB%91ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t-c%E1%BB%AFu-v%C3%A3ng-Thanh-Th%C3%A0nh-huy%E1%BB%87n-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-h%C3%B4n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-tOjO0Di9gTNk8O5AR-T78Q">Lãng Châu đông lâu diên phụng tống thập nhất cữu vãng Thanh Thành huyện, đắc hôn tự - 閬州東樓筵奉送十一舅往青城縣，得昏字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-canh-th%C3%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ho%C3%A0ng-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Thi%C3%AAn-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ph%E1%BB%A7-Tr%C3%B9ng-Quang-cung/poem-ZZV4u8Bf6GqthM_muVi-_Q">Phụng canh thái thượng hoàng ngự chế đề Thiên Trường phủ Trùng Quang cung - 奉賡太上皇御製題天長府重光宮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quan/Quan-x%C3%A1/poem-GuO4NZaPdI-t2Yrxg-oBfg">Quan xá - 官舍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quan/author-d-1pm3Y_z3pZB1_Ki_fHXg">Trần Quan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%ABa-Th%E1%BA%A9m-b%C3%A1t-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BB%B9-thi%E1%BB%87n-b%E1%BB%99-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-tr%E1%BB%9F-v%C5%A9-v%E1%BB%8B-to%E1%BA%A1i-tr%C3%AC-h%E1%BA%A1-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%AD-thi/poem-rhRx6w9jswcvvfgNflryhQ">Thừa Thẩm bát trượng Đông Mỹ thiện bộ viên ngoại, trở vũ vị toại trì hạ, phụng ký thử thi - 承沈八丈東美除膳部員外，阻雨未遂馳賀，奉寄此詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/T%E1%BB%91ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Gi%